spec_data.Name: rubygem-multipart
spec_data.Description:
Multipart is a gem that adds support to multipart/form-encoded and
multipart/mixed (file upload) to Net::HTTP::Post.  Nothing more, nothing less.
Currently it supports a file param with multiple files, but not multiple file
params.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 04:47:20 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Add multipart (file upload) support to Net::HTTP::Post
